title: Traveling during hurricane season? Here's what you should know
description: From what to pack to whether travel insurance will cover you, here’s what you need to know about travelling during tropical cyclones.
content:
This article was produced by National Geographic Traveller (UK).
Long balmy days, sparkling turquoise waters these are the classic ingredients of a tropical break. But risk going during the hurrican… [+6008 chars]
de: Reisen Sie während der Hurrikansaison? Folgendes sollten Sie wissen: Von dem, was Sie einpacken sollten, bis hin zur Frage, ob eine Reiseversicherung Sie abdeckt: Hier finden Sie alles, was Sie über Reisen während tropischer Wirbelstürme wissen müssen.
en: Traveling during hurricane season? Here's what you should know. From what to pack to whether travel insurance will cover you, here’s what you need to know about travelling during tropical cyclones.
la: Iter in tempore tempestatis? Hic est quod scias. Ex quo stipant ad an assecurationis itinerarium teget, hic est quid scire debes de peregrinationibus in cyclis tropicis.
